data.description: Welcome to your own piece of paradise in the beautiful well established neighborhood of Marsh Point located in Litchfield Beach. This immaculate, well maintained raised beach style home offers 3BR, 3.5BA and sits on a beautiful landscaped lot in a quiet cul-de-sac with marsh creek views from your back deck or your private oasis around the pool area. The main floor consists of Antique heartpine flooring throughout, half bath, laundry area, kitchen with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops, living/dining combo, den/study with fireplace off of main living area that opens to the back deck, spacious master bedroom with his & her walk-in closets, and sunroom overlooking pool area, large master bath with granite countertops and vessel sinks. Second floor consists of two bedrooms with Jack and Jill bathroom and granite countertops. Two car garage underneath with outdoor shower, workshop, storage and plenty of room for relaxation and entertainment.  Conveniently located to beaches, restaurants, golf and shopping.
